== Digital ==
* [https://bukovsky-archive.com/ '''Soviet Archives'''] (1999), compiled by Vladimir Bukovsky, prepared for publication by the late '''Julia Zaks''' (1938–2014) and Leonid Chernikhov. An online archive containing photocopies of over seven hundred classified documents, two hundred of which are available in English translation.

